TopicTitle: Who would win in a fight?

Articles.Content: Q of the Q Continuum retcons everything (including anything that could possibly defeat him in the future) out of existence.
The others in the Q Continuum, as they can strip him of his powers and leave him helpless.

Commander Shepard.

His/her renegade interrupt is so powerful the Q do not dare even touch him/her.

Emperor Palpatine.

The dark side of the force is more powerful than ever.
Hal-9000 saves "Bob" as ANSI instead of unicode, turning him into an incomprehensible string of characters.
